reviewText: My two year old son loves this!

AWESOME!!!!!  Love the ability this DVD has to simplify spelling for the kids.  They love it.  Most have learned some of the songs on the DVD to remember how to spell certain words or remember certain letters.

My 2 year old is a huge fan of word world. Since he's been watching the show, his speech and letter recognition has improved unbelievably. I will be buying more movies! It's an absolutely adorable show!
